What_We_Know__c:
22.04.2025:
Unfortunately at the moment we do not have a compatible build for Fedora 42, however a request can be submitted to our R&D team to build a compatible EPP client.  The customer requested that a compatible EPP client be build for Fedora 42.
Next_Steps__c:
23.04.2025:
A request for a Fedora 42 compatible build of EPP client for will be made.

25.04.2025:
Customer was informed about the new Netwrix Ideas Portal and have submitted their request on the new portal.  This case can be closed.
